title: 820-3332 Cycling.
message: No liquid damage. Board is cycling with fan up and down. Screen is coming on for a split second. Reflowed and resoldered U8900. No change. Replaced U8900 just to see if that might matter. No change. Is there any other direction to go with this board?

title: 820-3332 Cycling.
